metadata.name: Secret in the night
metadata.description: My work is largely inspired by strong women. I was very young when I first realized what it means to be a strong woman. My first and only idol today is my mother. I saw how much she works, how much she endures on herself, but with all this, she always remains a woman whose energy I want to recharge. It is always as warm with her as a bear in her bosom. There is nothing more intimate than the embodiment of a woman in the night!
